<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>情報検索台帳</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #f4f6fa;
      --panel: #ffffff;
      --line: #d7dee8;
      --text: #1f2937;
      --sub: #667085;
      --accent: #1f6feb;
      --accent-soft: #e8f1ff;
      --hover: #f8fbff;
      --selected: #eef5ff;
      --mark: #fff2a8;
      --shadow: 0 2px 10px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.06);
      --danger: #dc2626;
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    html, body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      font-family: "Yu Gothic UI", "Yu Gothic", "Meiryo", sans-serif;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    body {
      min-width: 1380px;
    }

    .page {
      width: 96%;
      max-width: 1800px;
      margin: 18px auto;
    }

    .top-panel {
      background: var(--panel);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 14px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      padding: 18px 20px 16px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .title-row {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: end;
      gap: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }

    .title-wrap h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 28px;
      line-height: 1.2;
      color: #0f172a;
    }

    .title-wrap p {
      margin: 6px 0 0;
      color: var(--sub);
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    .meta-box {
      text-align: right;
      color: var(--sub);
      font-size: 13px;
      min-width: 320px;
    }

    .meta-box strong {
      color: #0f172a;
    }

    .search-row {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 110px 110px;
      gap: 10px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .search-row input {
      height: 44px;
      border: 1px solid #c8d2df;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 0 14px;
      font-size: 15px;
      outline: none;
      background: #fff;
    }

    .search-row input:focus {
      border-color: var(--accent);
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(31, 111, 235, 0.12);
    }

    .btn {
      height: 44px;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 10px;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 700;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .btn-search {
      background: var(--accent);
      color: #fff;
    }

    .btn-clear {
      background: #64748b;
      color: #fff;
    }

    .status-row {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      margin-top: 10px;
      color: var(--sub);
      font-size: 13px;
      min-height: 24px;
    }

    .status-wrap {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 16px;
    }

    .status {
      color: var(--accent);
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .error {
      color: var(--danger);
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .main {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 560px 1fr;
      gap: 16px;
      min-height: 760px;
    }

    .panel {
      background: var(--panel);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 14px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .panel-header {
      padding: 14px 16px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
      background: #fbfcfe;
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #0f172a;
    }

    .list-toolbar {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 10px 16px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e7edf5;
      background: #fcfdff;
      color: var(--sub);
      font-size: 13px;
      min-height: 46px;
    }

    .list-scroll {
      overflow-y: auto;
      height: calc(760px - 52px - 46px - 66px);
      background: #fcfdff;
    }

    .list-item {
      padding: 14px 16px 12px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e8edf4;
      cursor: pointer;
      background: #fff;
      transition: background 0.15s ease, border-color 0.15s ease;
    }

    .list-item:hover {
      background: var(--hover);
    }

    .list-item.selected {
      background: var(--selected);
      border-left: 4px solid var(--accent);
      padding-left: 12px;
    }

    .item-title {
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 700;
      line-height: 1.5;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      color: #0f172a;
      word-break: break-word;
    }

    .chips {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 6px;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .chip {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 3px 9px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: #eef2f7;
      color: #334155;
      font-size: 12px;
      line-height: 1.4;
    }

    .item-preview {
      color: #475467;
      line-height: 1.7;
      min-height: 46px;
      white-space: pre-wrap;
      word-break: break-word;
    }

    .item-footer {
      margin-top: 10px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #667085;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .pager {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 6px;
      padding: 14px 12px;
      border-top: 1px solid #e7edf5;
      background: #fbfcfe;
      min-height: 66px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .pager-btn {
      min-width: 40px;
      height: 36px;
      padding: 0 12px;
      border: 1px solid #cad5e2;
      border-radius: 8px;
      background: #fff;
      color: #334155;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .pager-btn:hover:not(:disabled) {
      background: #f3f7ff;
      border-color: #9dbcf5;
    }

    .pager-btn.active {
      background: var(--accent);
      border-color: var(--accent);
      color: #fff;
    }

    .pager-btn:disabled {
      cursor: default;
      opacity: 0.45;
      background: #f8fafc;
    }

    .pager-ellipsis {
      padding: 0 4px;
      color: #94a3b8;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .empty-box {
      padding: 48px 24px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #667085;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }

    .detail-scroll {
      overflow-y: auto;
      height: calc(760px - 52px);
      padding: 18px 20px 24px;
      background: #fff;
    }

    .detail-title {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 700;
      line-height: 1.5;
      margin: 0 0 14px;
      color: #0f172a;
      word-break: break-word;
    }

    .detail-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 170px 1fr;
      gap: 10px 14px;
      margin-bottom: 22px;
      padding-bottom: 20px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e6ebf2;
    }

    .detail-label {
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #344054;
      padding-top: 2px;
    }

    .detail-value {
      color: #1f2937;
      line-height: 1.8;
      white-space: pre-wrap;
      word-break: break-word;
    }

    .detail-section {
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .detail-section h3 {
      margin: 0 0 10px;
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #0f172a;
      padding-left: 10px;
      border-left: 4px solid var(--accent);
    }

    .detail-box {
      background: #fbfcff;
      border: 1px solid #e6ebf2;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 14px 16px;
      line-height: 1.8;
      white-space: pre-wrap;
      word-break: break-word;
      min-height: 56px;
    }

    .placeholder {
      padding: 60px 20px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #667085;
      line-height: 1.9;
    }

    mark {
      background: var(--mark);
      padding: 0 2px;
      border-radius: 2px;
    }

    a {
      color: var(--accent);
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="page">
    <section class="top-panel">
      <div class="title-row">
        <div class="title-wrap">
          <h1>情報検索台帳</h1>
          <p>既存の SharePoint リスト情報を検索・閲覧するための専用画面</p>
        </div>
        <div class="meta-box">
          <div>対象リスト: <strong id="targetListName"></strong></div>
          <div id="targetListNote"></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="search-row">
        <input
          type="text"
          id="keywordInput"
          placeholder="キーワードを入力（スペース区切りでAND検索）"
        />
        <button class="btn btn-search" id="searchBtn" type="button">検索</button>
        <button class="btn btn-clear" id="clearBtn" type="button">クリア</button>
      </div>

      <div class="status-row">
        <div>
          表示件数: <strong id="resultCount">0</strong> 件
        </div>
        <div class="status-wrap">
          <span class="status" id="statusText"></span>
          <span class="error" id="errorText"></span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="main">
      <div class="panel">
        <div class="panel-header">一覧</div>

        <div class="list-toolbar">
          <div id="pageSummary">0 件</div>
          <div id="pageInfo">0 / 0 ページ</div>
        </div>

        <div class="list-scroll" id="listArea"></div>

        <div class="pager" id="pagerArea"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="panel">
        <div class="panel-header">詳細</div>
        <div class="detail-scroll" id="detailArea">
          <div class="placeholder">
            左の一覧からデータを選択すると、<br />
            詳細内容がここに表示されます。
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>

  <script src="./js/info-search-ledger.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
